```

### How it looks:

* Uses **hexadecimal** (0‚Äì9, a‚Äìf)
* Written with colons (`:`)
* Much longer than IPv4

### Big advantage of IPv6 ‚úÖ

IPv6 can create:

> **340 undecillion addresses**
> (that‚Äôs more than enough for every device on Earth‚Ä¶ and more)

